Directions:\
1. Marinate Steak In a large shallow bowl or resealable plastic bag, whisk together balsamic vinegar, Worcestershire sauce, and 2 tablespoons olive oil until fully combined. Pat steaks dry with paper towel. Add steaks to marinade and turn to coat. Set aside to marinate at room temperature for about 10 minutes.\
