5. Toast Baguettes Wipe pan from steaks clean and place over medium heat. Halve baguettes lengthwise, and add to pan cut-side down. Toast until golden, working in batches if needed, 4-5 minutes. Remove and slather toasted sides with horseradish sauce.\
