6. Plate Sandwiches Drain cucumbers and return to bowl. Add basil and 1 tablespoon olive oil, tossing to coat. Slice steaks against the grain as thinly as possible (see Recipe Tip). Divide steak, tomatoes, and arugula evenly between baguettes, then halve on a diagonal. Serve sandwiches with pickled cucumber.\
